indiquée est deaconess à Gerresheim, Düsseldorf, Nordrhein-Westfalen, Allemagne. Elle est décédée après 2 octobre 1347."},"de":{"1290–after 2 October 1347":"1290–nach 2. Oktober 1347","1284–1339":"1284–1339","1290–1347":"1290–1347","1295–1391":"1295–1391","1295–Female":"1295–Verstorben","1275–1312":"1275–1312","1312–1356":"1312–1356","1270–1330":"1270–1330","1270–Female":"1270–Verstorben","2 October 1347":"2. Oktober 1347","1330":"1330","1275":"1275","1295":"1295","1284":"1284","1270":"1270","1391":"1391","1290":"1290","1347":"1347","1312":"1312","1356":"1356","27 October 1312":"27. Oktober 1312","after 2 October 1347":"nach 2. Oktober 1347","1339":"1339","Netherlands":"Niederlande","Dussen, Noord-Brabant, Nederland":"Dussen, Nord-Brabant, Niederlande","Gerresheim, Düsseldorf, North Rhine-Westphalia, Germany":"Gerresheim, Düsseldorf, Nordrhein-Westfalen, Deutschland","Nederland":"Niederlande","Tervuren, Duchy of Brabant, Holy Roman Empire":"Tervuren, Brabant, Belgien","lifeSummary":"Als Dame Elsbeen van Wijtvliet 1290 in Dussen, Nord-Brabant, Niederlande geboren wurde, war ihr Vater Ridder Willem Arnoud Heyman van der Sluyse van Doveren 21 und ihre Mutter Geertruijd Willem Jan Willem van Wijffliet 21. Sie hatte mit Jean I I Le Pacifique De Vreedzame DE BRABANT mindestens 1 Sohn. 1347, als sie 57 Jahre alt war, war ihr Beruf als deaconess in Gerresheim, Düsseldorf, Nordrhein-Westfalen, Deutschland aufgeführt. Sie starb nach 2. Oktober 1347."},"ht":{"1290–after 2 October 1347":"1290–after 2 October 1347","1284–1339":"1284–1339","1290–1347":"1290–1347","1295–1391":"1295–1391","1295–Female":"1295–Desede","1275–1312":"1275–1312","1312–1356":"1312–1356","1270–1330":"1270–1330","1270–Female":"1270–Desede","2 October 1347":"2 October 1347","1330":"1330","1275":"1275","1295":"1295","1284":"1284","1270":"1270","1391":"1391","1290":"1290","1347":"1347","1312":"1312","1356":"1356","27 October 1312":"27 October 1312","after 2 October 1347":"after 2 October 1347","1339":"1339","N